OL,3,CFundraiser for police officer who lost
OL,4,Cfamily in Boxing Day fire tops #250k
OL,6,FAn appeal to raise funds for a police
OL,7,Fofficer who lost his wife and two
OL,8,Fchildren in a Boxing Day house fire
OL,9,Fhas topped #250,000.
OL,11,FFionnghuala Shearman, known as Nu,
OL,12,Fdied alongside her daughter Eve,
OL,13,Fseven, and four-year-old son Ohner in
OL,14,Fthe fire at their home in Brimscombe,
OL,15,Fnear Stroud, Gloucestershire.
