OL,3,CFundraiser for police officer who lost
OL,4,Cfamily in Boxing Day fire tops #250k
OL,6,FTom Shearman, an officer with
OL,7,FGloucestershire Constabulary, was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital after his attempts
OL,9,Fto rescue his family were beaten back
OL,10,Fby the severity of the fire but has
OL,11,Fbeen discharged.
OL,13,FThe GoFundMe fundraising appeal, which
OL,14,Fwas launched on Sunday, passed its
OL,15,Ftarget of #110,000, with a fresh aim
OL,16,Fof #350,000.
OL,18,FEarly on Wednesday, the figure had
OL,19,Freached more than #255,000 with more
OL,20,Fthan 12,200 donations.
