OL,6,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,7,Fmid-terrace Cotswold stone cottage on
OL,8,FBrimscombe Hill at about 3am on Boxing
OL,9,FDay.
OL,11,FMr and Mrs Shearman had been awoken by
OL,12,Fthe fire and had attempted to reach
OL,13,Ftheir children in the rear bedroom.
OL,15,FThe police officer smashed a bathroom
OL,16,Fwindow to try to access his children's
OL,17,Froom from outside but was unable to do
OL,18,Fso and could not regain entry to the
OL,19,Fhouse through the bathroom window.
