OL,6,FPolice believe the fire started on the
OL,7,Fground floor and investigations were
OL,8,Fongoing to establish the cause, but it
OL,9,Fwas not being treated as suspicious.
OL,11,FThe fire destroyed the roof, the
OL,12,Fceilings and stairs, as well as
OL,13,Fcausing other significant internal
OL,14,Fdamage.
OL,16,FTemporary Chief Constable Maggie Blyth
OL,17,Fsaid the bodies of the two children
OL,18,Fand the family dog had been recovered
OL,19,Ffrom the property.
